quran[24{c,v,t}:
37,103,aakhir ko jab inn dono ne sir tasleem khham kar diya aur ibrahim ne betay ko maathay ke bil gira diya
37,104,"aur hum ne nida di ke"" ae ibrahim"
37,105,to ne khawab sach kar dekhaya hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
37,106,"yaqeenan yeh aik khuli azmaish thi """
37,107,aur hum ne aik barri qurbani fidyay mein day kar is bachay ko churra liya
37,108,aur is ki tareef o tauseef hamesha ke liye baad ki naslon mein chore di
37,109,salam hai ibrahim par
37,110,hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
37,111,yaqeenan woh hamaray momin bundon mein se tha
37,112,"aur hum ne usay ishaq ki basharat di, aik nabi salheen mein se"
37,113,aur usay aur ishaq ko barket di ab un dono ki zaryat mein se koi mohsin hai aur koi apne nafs par Sarih zulm karne wala hai
37,114,aur hum ne moose o haroon par ahsaan kya
37,115,unn ko aur un ki qoum ko karb azeem se nijaat di
37,116,unhen nusrat bakhsh jis ki wajah se wohi ghalib rahay
37,117,un ko nihayat wazeh kitaab ataa ki
37,118,inhen raah raast dikhayi
37,119,aur baad ki naslon mein un ka zikar kher baqi rakha
37,120,salam hai moose aur haroon par
37,121,hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
37,122,Dur haqeeqat woh hamaray momin bundon mein se thay
37,123,aur ilyas bhi yaqeenan mursaleen mein se tha
37,124,"yaad karo jab is ne apni qoum se kaha tha ke"" tum log drtay nahi ho ?"
37,125,kya tum b - al ko pkarte ho aur Ahsen ul Khalqeen ko chore dete ho
37,126,"uss Allah ko jo tumhara aur tumahray aglay pichlle aaba o ajdaad ka rab hai? """
